Create lib/pag_server_web/live/workspace_chat/message_list.ex as function component. Scrollable container with phx-hook='AutoScrollTranscript' for auto-scroll. Iterates @entries (pre-merged messages + tool calls from helpers.chat_entries). Delegates to message_bubble/tool_call_card/approval_banner based on entry type. Shows streaming_state as live-updating assistant bubble at bottom. Empty state when no messages ('Start a conversation...'). Load earlier button at top for pagination.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Scrollable container with auto-scroll hook
- Iterates entries and delegates to correct sub-component
- Streaming state renders as live bubble
- Empty state shown when no messages
- Load earlier button at top